{"id": "1423595395375824928", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "高難易度は別としてストーリー上だと界域染めにバフォダフ貰った方が結果的に毒の付与数高くなりそうかねー？", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T08:59:51.381000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
