{"id": "1423599607887433830", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "リリーちゃんの可能性を模索しておりますけれども現状は残念ながら…😭", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T09:16:35.722000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423599685947359252", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "ちなみに今リッツの強さに心ときめいております。毒最強💪😁", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T09:16:54.333000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "chiiin", "emoji_id": "1390953055800791232", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423600388283699221", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1174685020217151548", "author_name": "yasaizujusu", "author_bot": false, "content": "毒楽しそうなんだよな〜〜〜〜〜〜かなり気になっています", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T09:19:41.783000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423601250104246312", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "私毒の強みとして、敵が覚醒状態に移行しても毒自体の効果が切れない事が強いと思うんですよぅ…。え、切れませんよね？？（無知）", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T09:23:07.257000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😮", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423602317873123378", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1174685020217151548", "author_name": "yasaizujusu", "author_bot": false, "content": "切れなかったらかなり強そう、ただ覚醒する奴らって大体後半バケモンみたいな火力出してくるから、その攻撃に耐えられるかどうか…", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T09:27:21.833000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423652121135550535", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "279045292639387648", "author_name": "horydragon", "author_bot": false, "content": "敵覚醒でも毒は残りますよー", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T12:45:15.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423661344447660052", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "どうもリッツ使いです\n敵の覚醒では切れません、分裂されるとなぜか消えます\nちなみにリッツの緑炎は刺突ダメージなので覚醒ターンの無敵を無視して殴り倒せます、オススメ！", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T13:21:54.865000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1032734003712774174"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1423601250104246312", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423662802261901457", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "リッツは１Ｔ中に一気に付与する毒の量が大きいからリリーとは相性良いかもしれない、純次元の方が強い説もあるのですが…", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T13:27:42.435000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🎉", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🙌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423666744853008395", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "721000392724578355", "author_name": "hexetrygon_bickelli", "author_bot": false, "content": "覚醒ターン無視できるの知らんかった　覚醒体相手の対策になるのか", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T13:43:22.422000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423691089948311582", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "518778434432925706", "author_name": "lele_fi", "author_bot": false, "content": "首切りの一撃のダメージ計算ってどうなってるかわかる方いますか？\n効果値0%の首切りが163ダメ\n効果値20%の首切りが189ダメで16%しかダメUPしてない気がして\nステータス画面での首切りの一撃素点158点なので158×1.2＝189.6でそれっぽいんですけど\nそれだと編成時のダメージ強化が今度は乗ってなくて謎です", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T15:20:06.745000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423691089239609435", "filename": "G2V__QWawAAZj-b.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1709220, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1423691089239609435/G2V__QWawAAZj-b.png?ex=6a340ca6&is=6a32bb26&hm=0b285f46e244f69d68b47b07cfd9012250cbaab9f0d403dd43ed85ede32eee23&"}, {"id": "1423691089650384946", "filename": "G2V_2TJasAAKnSd.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1454644, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1423691089650384946/G2V_2TJasAAKnSd.png?ex=6a340ca6&is=6a32bb26&hm=b71986d58fee2218f7e1fc907d30689c690987f87b6be6f356e0eb979f7ae141&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423711235509190697", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "リッツ使い助かります🙇‍♀️海で還元しようと試しに使ってみたら使い勝手良すぎない？？って今日初めてリッツの強さに惹かれちゃいました( ⸝⸝ ᴖ.ᴖ ⸝⸝ ) 被ダメが気になるジェンキンと違って比較的安定して立ち回れるリッツちゃん強いです〜‼️🙌✨ 何かと刺突便利ですもんね。回れ回れのあの鋭いバレエ靴で突き刺してるのかしら😶❔", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T16:40:09.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["247960263599325186"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1423662802261901457", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423750625669288016", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "界域知識数×0.05倍上昇は一度ビーコン（超次元内）に入れてあげる事で効果を発揮するからそれかもです。ダメ強自体は戦闘中に素点からしっかりと倍率が乗っていました。", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T19:16:41.167000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423755199838683186", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "518778434432925706", "author_name": "lele_fi", "author_bot": false, "content": "界域知識0で検証してたのでビーコンは入ってないはずです\n仮にビーコンまで入ってたらさらに倍率が出てないことになっちゃうので...\n表記通りの倍率だと200ダメくらいにはなるはずなんですけど", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T19:34:51.734000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1032734003712774174"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1423750625669288016", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423757847036035263", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "Leleさんの編成時のチーム情報がないので何とも…🙄💭 ぉぉぉ調査班任せました💪💪", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T19:45:22.875000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["518778434432925706"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1423755199838683186", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423762391455236127", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "518778434432925706", "author_name": "lele_fi", "author_bot": false, "content": "一応PTこれですね、変なデバフはないはずなんですが...\n山一周回して引き直しても倍率変わらず(8.5%up)\n有識者お願いします🙏", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T20:03:26.349000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423762390637346946", "filename": "1759495216-ZV2UqX49mlEIA6nPeofRHi7y.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 840762, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1423762390637346946/1759495216-ZV2UqX49mlEIA6nPeofRHi7y.png?ex=6a344f0e&is=6a32fd8e&hm=a7b75cba7a0223867107a3869648f653cf0b8addf48ab6992f25b8fc04e16494&"}, {"id": "1423762391153250476", "filename": "1759521225-cr6oxhsgBIbSRdYy4DqwfW23.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1640059, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1423762391153250476/1759521225-cr6oxhsgBIbSRdYy4DqwfW23.png?ex=6a344f0e&is=6a32fd8e&hm=f8bcd0bd82ae012ce3d67c5fdf6de4ace86e91fbcde797f3c284641613df641c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423777787914883184", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "考えられる線としては13%として処理されるのではなく、“基礎ダメージ”から10%（首狩り）と3%（ダメ強）を別に計算してる気がしますね。後はダメージは小数点切り上げだけど、バフによる上昇分は切り捨てとか…ぶつぶつ ‪🥲‎‪🥲‎‪🥲‎ﾑｽﾞｶｼｲ でも明らかに20%から乗ってないですよね🙄", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T21:04:37.151000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-03T21:30:23.373000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423795263142760458", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "界域盛ってなくても、入れて出したらビーコンはつきますが、すごい数値低くなるのでそのせいかな", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T22:14:03.570000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-03T22:14:42.602000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423796661360136203", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "158→3%のダメ強=+4.74\n158→10%の基礎ダメ増=+15.8\nありえるとしたら、4と15で計算してるかな？\nそしたら158+19だから177", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T22:19:36.931000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1423800415794892902", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "上の画像の20%増加は意味わからんね\nデバフくらってね？", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T22:34:32.058000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
